original_title: Namie Amuro 25th Anniverary Live in Okinawa
overview: On September 16, 2017 a special two day outdoor concert was held in Amuro's hometown, Okinawa, at Ginowan Seaside Park. A few days on September 20, 2017 she publicly announced her plans to retire from the music industry in a year's time.  This concert was included in all editions of the Final Tour 2018 which was released on DVD and Blu-ray on August 29, 2018
title: Namie Amuro 25th Anniverary Live in Okinawa
